      <title>Bath & Body Works 预计全年销售和利润因需求放缓而黯淡</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/bath-body-works-projects-downbeat-fy-sales-profit-slowing-demand-2024-02-29/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴斯&amp; Body Works 周四预测年度销售额和利润低于分析师预期，原因是消费者缩减了蜡烛和香水等非必需品的支出，导致该公司股价在盘前交易中下跌 9%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/bath-body-works-projects-downbeat-fy-sales-profit-slowing-demand-2024-02-29/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Feb 2024 13:58:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
