    <item>
      <title>美国1月份通胀增幅符合预期</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/us-inflation-increases-line-with-expectations-january-2024-02-29/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国一月份物价有所回升，但通胀年度增幅却是近三年来最小，这使得美联储六月份降息的可能性仍然存在。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/us-inflation-increases-line-with-expectations-january-2024-02-29/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Feb 2024 13:49:59 GMT</pubDate>
