      <title>特斯拉必须面对 6,000 名员工在种族偏见案件中提出的集体诉讼</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/legal/tesla-must-face-class-action-claims-by-6000-workers-race-bias-case-2024-02-29/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加州一名法官初步裁定，近 6,000 名黑人工厂工人可以集体起诉特斯拉，因为该电动汽车制造商涉嫌未能解决弗里蒙特工厂猖獗的种族歧视和骚扰问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/legal/tesla-must-face-class-action-claims-by-6000-workers-race-bias-case-2024-02-29/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Feb 2024 13:43:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
